Sentencas: In the present study, we have investigated the effect of La3+, Pr3+, and Sm3+ triple-doping on structural, electrical, and thermal properties of ceria (Ce1-x(Lax/3Prx/3Smx/3)O2-delta).
Titulo: Effect of La3+, Pr3+, and Sm3+ triple-doping on structural, electrical, and thermal properties of ceria solid electrolytes for intermediate temperature solid oxide fuel cells

Sentencas: X-ray diffraction studies confirm the formation of samples with single-phase cubic-fluorite structure (JCPDS PDF File No: 34-0394).
Titulo: Effect of La3+, Pr3+, and Sm3+ triple-doping on structural, electrical, and thermal properties of ceria solid electrolytes for intermediate temperature solid oxide fuel cells

Sentencas: The lattice parameter values increases with increasing the dopant concentration (from 5.4190 angstrom to 5.4503 angstrom)
Titulo: Effect of La3+, Pr3+, and Sm3+ triple-doping on structural, electrical, and thermal properties of ceria solid electrolytes for intermediate temperature solid oxide fuel cells

Sentencas: All the prepared samples were sintered at 1300 degrees C for 4 h. The values of relative densities were found to be higher than 95% and the high value is observed for the composition LPS8 i.e. 97.8%.
Titulo: Effect of La3+, Pr3+, and Sm3+ triple-doping on structural, electrical, and thermal properties of ceria solid electrolytes for intermediate temperature solid oxide fuel cells

Sentencas: The calculated crystalline size values were found to be in the range of 46 and 53 nm.
Titulo: Effect of La3+, Pr3+, and Sm3+ triple-doping on structural, electrical, and thermal properties of ceria solid electrolytes for intermediate temperature solid oxide fuel cells

Sentencas: Scanning electron microscope and energy dispersive spectroscopic techniques reveal the surface-microstructure and presence of elemental confirmation in the compositions.

Sentencas: The average grain size values were found to be in between 231 and 366 nm.

Sentencas: Raman spectroscopy study reveals the existence of oxygen vacancies in all the compositions and estimated concentration of oxygen vacancies is found to be high for LPS8 composition.
Titulo: Effect of La3+, Pr3+, and Sm3+ triple-doping on structural, electrical, and thermal properties of ceria solid electrolytes for intermediate temperature solid oxide fuel cells

Sentencas: The impedance spectroscopy revealed the total ionic conductivity and activation energies of all the compositions.
Titulo: Effect of La3+, Pr3+, and Sm3+ triple-doping on structural, electrical, and thermal properties of ceria solid electrolytes for intermediate temperature solid oxide fuel cells

Sentencas: The composition Ce0.76La0.08Pr0.08Sm0.08O2-delta (LPS8) displays the highest total ionic conductivity i.e. 0.043 S/cm with low activation energy i.e. 0.76 eV. Matched thermal expansion coefficient of the sample Ce0.76La0.08Pr0.08Sm0.08O2-delta with already existing electrode materials, makes it as an effective electrolyte material for the intermediate temperature-solid oxide fuel cell applications.
